			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px; height: 150px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Emblem_of_Syria_(2025%E2%80%93present)_variation_outline_(money).svg" class="mw-file-description" title="Variation of the emblem of Syria with heavy outline/stroke used in currencies (2026–present)"><img alt="Variation of the emblem of Syria with heavy outline/stroke used in currencies (2026–present)" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/Emblem_of_Syria_%282025%E2%80%93present%29_variation_outline_%28money%29.svg/120px-Emblem_of_Syria_%282025%E2%80%93present%29_variation_outline_%28money%29.svg.png" decoding="async" width="120" height="90" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/43/Emblem_of_Syria_%282025%E2%80%93present%29_variation_outline_%28money%29.svg/250px-Emblem_of_Syria_%282025%E2%80%93present%29_variation_outline_%28money%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="676" data-file-height="509"></a></span></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">Variation of the emblem of Syria with heavy outline/stroke used in currencies (<b>2026–present</b>)</div>
		</li>
</ul>
